// Elopement-in-Siurana landing — shared component used by
// /elopement-siurana (CA), /es/elopement-siurana (ES), /en/elopement-siurana (EN).
//
// Evergreen, indexable service page (Schema.org Service + FAQPage +
// Breadcrumb) targeting "elopement Siurana" / "fotografo elopement Tarragona"
// and the international-traveller elopement niche. All copy keyed by `lang`.
//
// Photos come from the real Maria & Robert elopement. They are pulled from
// PHOTOS['elopement-siurana'] (photos.generated.ts) once Eric drops the
// "Maria&Robert-*.JPG" originals in the shared drive and re-runs
// scripts/process-photos.mjs. Until then the gallery falls back to the
// existing real Siurana photos so the page still renders — no code change is
// needed when the real set lands.

